content: I write contracts on solidity:- tokens of almost any complexity;- contracts for presale;- airdrop contract;- contracts for ICO;- forks of safemoon, safejet and any other defi protocols;- I will fork pancakeswap, uniswap, goosefi and any other *swap (contracts + frontend).I can make a contract from scratch or make the changes you need, add functions, change the logic.I make contracts for networks:-Ethereum-Binance Smart Chain-Cosmos/Matic-and everything else that evm supports.If necessary, I will help you to deploy and verify.Write to me in telegram: @Anton_woowhttps://t.me/Anton_woow
